nt="v1" itunes:key="L66"><span begin="03:41.948" end="03:42.256">I've</span> <span begin="03:42.256" end="03:42.527">been</span> <span begin="03:42.527" end="03:42.801">dream</span><span begin="03:42.801" end="03:43.362">in',</span> <span begin="03:44.231" end="03:45.390">dream</span><span begin="03:45.390" end="03:45.733">in'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直梦见你，一直</span></p></div></body></tt>